{"name":"Jardinière Salad","slug":"jardiniere-salad","description":"The perfect picnic-style summer salad.","ingredients":[{"name":"carrots","quantity":"10 - 15","additionalInstruction":"peeled and coarsely chopped"},{"name":"bell peppers","quantity":"2","additionalInstruction":"coarsely chopped"},{"name":"small head cauliflower","quantity":"1","additionalInstruction":"chopped into small florets"},{"name":"small head broccoli","quantity":"1","additionalInstruction":"chopped into small florets"},{"name":"red onion","quantity":"<sup>1</sup>&frasl;<sub>2</sub>","additionalInstruction":"thickly sliced"},{"name":"whole button mushrooms","quantity":"8 oz (225 g)","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"white balsamic vinegar","quantity":"<sup>1</sup>&frasl;<sub>2</sub> cup","additionalInstruction":"or your favourite vinegar"},{"name":"water","quantity":"<sup>1</sup>&frasl;<sub>2</sub> cup","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"Italian Dressing","quantity":"1 - 2 tbsp","additionalInstruction":"or prepared Epicure Balsamic Vinaigrette"},{"name":"Italian Dressing Mix","quantity":"2 tbsp","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"oil","quantity":"<sup>3</sup>&frasl;<sub>4</sub> cup","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"white vinegar","quantity":"<sup>1</sup>&frasl;<sub>4</sub> cup","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"black or green olives","quantity":"1 cup","additionalInstruction":"- optional"}],"totalTime":"25 min","servings":"10 servings","preparation":["Pour about 2 cups water into a large pot. Bring to a boil over high heat. Add carrots and steam for 4 minutes, then add peppers, cauliflower, broccoli, onion and mushrooms. Steam for 5–7 more minutes, until tender-crisp.","Meanwhile, whisk white balsamic vinegar with water and Italian Dressing.","Drain vegetables and place in a large bowl. Drizzle with dressing. Add olives if desired, and toss to mix.","Refrigerate salad for at least 4 hours or overnight, until well-chilled. Store in refrigerator for up to 5 days."],"tag